Allow users to input information about their major, interests, level of education, current employment.
Allow users to search for others based on their inputted information.
Allow users to send personal messages directly to other users
Allow users to create messaging boards with other select users to exchange messages
Allow users to contact customer service if they stumble upon a problem
Users can report other users if someone is violating the rules that is causing toxicity or conducting inappropriate behaviors.
Recommend groups/users to new users that may be of interest to them or can help them with what they are looking for out of the app.
Allow users to edit their profile if/when they need to.
